This paper is primarily focused on image retrieval, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) categories. The paper also proposes a deep learning model that combines global and local features, which is a topic of interest in the machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) fields. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of autoencoder-based dimensionality reduction, which is a technique commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL).
